    "Although recommended, generalizability is not always within reach due to ethics, budgeting, and many more considerations in data sharing.",
    "Hence, hospital collaborations using modelcustomization techniques are needed to translate site-specific trained models to new contexts, else generalizability remains seldom practiced in literature. 2.",
    "Prospective Cohorts.",
    "Data assessment of recruited subjects before outcomes, thus proving temporality, is a core factor in asserting causality.",
    "A prospective design is valued more highly in the evidence pyramid than a retrospective one (historical cohort) in which events have already occurred."
